test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (3 == 3 and 3 == 3 and 2 == 3)
 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ad9eb4c2d80>([83])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ad9eb4c2d80> = [[1, 83], [1, 83, 1], [83], [83, 1], [1, 83], [1, 83, 1], ...].count
 +  and   3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ad9eb4c2d80>([1, 83])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ad9eb4c2d80> = [[1, 83], [1, 83, 1], [83], [83, 1], [1, 83], [1, 83, 1], ...].count
 +  and   2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ad9eb4c2d80>([83, 1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ad9eb4c2d80> = [[1, 83], [1, 83, 1], [83], [83, 1], [1, 83], [1, 83, 1], ...].count
